GetSimple is an XML based, stand-a-alone, fully independant and lite Content Management System.. After the installation please open Safari and open the side 'http://your_ios_device/dokuwiki/getsimple'.
 GetSimple is an XML based, stand-a-alone, fully independant and lite Content Management System.
 
 With the cydia packages below you can use GetSimple CMS: 
 - 'atv-lighttpd-php-mysql' for AppleTV
 - 'ios-lighttpd-php-mysql' for iPhone/iPad
 - 'touch-lighttpd-php-mysql' for iPhone/iPad
   (For safety reasons, you should not use the touch- package)
 
 The package files will be stored at /var/www/getsimple
 During the installation the permission of some folders are set to the owner 'daemon:_www'. 
 
 Please open Safari at your iOS Device and type in 'http://localhost/getsimple'.
 (Please use Safari. I don't know why, but e.g. Chrome create some problems.)
 
 If you remove this package, please note that all content in /var/www/getsimple will be deleted.
 
 If you would like to get more package information, please have a look at http://goo.gl/LXfUB . 
 
